{"tid":82273,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"認真分析MK台妹余思霆拎華姐冠軍原因","createTime":"2017-01-15T21:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T07:45:54.000Z","uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d2c0878e1f8192d09c58594c34d6f6de0c4004","tid":82273,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T21:37:35.000Z","msg":"才藝表演個part真心我睇唔出有其他佳麗表演係好過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女盈玩埋D垃圾魔術唔洗討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本就唔算係才藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打鼓條女打到甩晒beat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n林宣妤娃娃舞叫做過得去啦 冇一種俾人覺得stunning既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n14號跳拉丁舞第一次睇係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實認真睇多次就覺得隻舞唔係難跳同冇咩特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n林宣妤輸俾佢係唔想做到主場就一定贏(？)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n港女盈冇身材冇才藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拎到第三都好好采<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打鼓條女預左冇獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不解釋<br />\n而我最想講既係14號輸俾佢係因為唔識講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反MK妹識講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (雖然問答係用普通話）<br />\n仲有14號其實把聲好撚蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nexact7ly係連登仔最憎既大陸西聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樣認真睇都係大陸味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至於大奶奶9號入唔到圍都係大陸味同唔識講廣東話出事<br />\n你地班連登仔見人大波少少就狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蝗味濃到咁都狗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸：14號就咁睇樣都OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一聽到把大陸西聲即刻turn off<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08be8cc4222d7c0d82cc14fe81c439ad740c5a51","tid":82273,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T21:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6qlmof9v\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6qlmof9v&h=9d3d5f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4f5b3962c9dfed6c5e0d2c94da6701bd04d0c5","tid":82273,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T21:41:16.000Z","msg":"求撚其啦你都無得屌"},{"pid":"c386999a5c1c1ba59c4382efc4b520a3ff7dd50a","tid":82273,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T00:28:04.000Z","msg":"腸左呢個post 先知又選香港小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606c55cc403c0901cc583577fd01f74027f2a125","tid":82273,"uid":28425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T00:36:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腸左呢個post 先知又選香港小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係華姐"},{"pid":"3faad628616d6eb1c4f34ced8ce276c1ce522fc1","tid":82273,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ca1a822783e0e878d9644d17d1ffe5f2c43667","tid":82273,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a3f58a929c1ec8dc7b83c0a43944b4c9dfb5e6","tid":82273,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s